	<p>I have heard the seru shard drops off regular legionaires and legionaires of the hand in Sanctus Seru.  They can be found wandering around the upper walk that goes around the city.  Can anyone confirm for me how rare they drop this and which seem to drop it more frequently.  I solo'd the area for about 3 hours last night without seeing one.  Plat was nice though and danger was minimal.  At 65, nothing assisted even if I was fighting on top of another guard.</p>
	
	
	
