	<p>If you take a exp group up there, and kill for about 2-3 hours, you should see 3-4 of them.  I am pretty sure he drops it and spawns in the same spot every time, but the groups I have gone in have always just gone in circles around the catwalk.  Great exp, and a fairly common drop.  The mobs say some really funny death lines, and also drop around 20pp coin each.</p>
	
	
	
