	<!-- message -->
	<p>Hey Georgina, welcome to the board! <img src="images/smilies/smile.gif" border="0" alt="" title="smile" smilieid="1" /><br />
<br />
There are actually 10 shards for the Vex Thal Key Quest that drop throught SoL.  You need a unique shard from the following 10 zones:<br />
<br />
Dawnshroud Peak  - soloed, took me about an hour<br />
Seru - soloed, 4th kill<br />
Sraa<br />
Maiden's Eye<br />
Scarlet Desert - buffed up a group hunting on the plateau and they let me loot one, was there about 30 minutes<br />
The Grey - first sun revenant I ever killed<br />
Akheva - soloed, 3d kill<br />
The Deep<br />
Fungus Grove<br />
Acrylia - won random on a guild raid on the way to Ring of Fire<br />
<br />
(My bank is CRYING with all this VT key quest, not to mention various PoP quest crap!)<br />
<br />
It's like the stupid VP key quest on steriods!  To complete the quest, you also need a glowing orb of luclinite (drops from nearly all SoL boss mobs) a piece from the Emperor (you have to complete an additional 4 part key quest just to get TO the emperor) and another thing I can't remember.</p>
	
	
	
